==提名及獲獎==
===奧斯卡金像獎===
電影在[[第29届奥斯卡金像奖|第29届奥斯卡金像奖]]中，獲提名9個[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡]]獎項，贏得5個。<ref name="Oscars1957">{{Cite web |url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/29th-winners.html |title=The 29th Academy Awards (1957) Nominees and Winners |accessdate=2011-08-21 |work=oscars.org |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110706094056/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/29th-winners.html |archivedate=2011-07-06 }}</ref><ref name="NY Times">{{cite news |url=http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/27374/The-King-and-I/awards |title=NY Times: The King and I |accessdate=2008-12-22 |work=NY Times |archive-date=2012-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121020120520/http://movies.nytimes.com/movie/27374/The-King-and-I/awards |dead-url=no }}</ref>

====獲獎====
* [[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|最佳男主角奖]] – [[尤·伯連納|尤·伯連納]]
* [[奥斯卡最佳艺术指导奖|最佳艺术指导奖]] – [[John_DeCuir|John DeCuir]], [[Lyle_R._Wheeler|Lyle R. Wheeler]], [[Walter_M._Scott|Walter M. Scott]], [[Paul_S._Fox|Paul S. Fox]]
* [[奥斯卡最佳服装设计奖|最佳服装设计奖]] – [[Irene_Sharaff|Irene Sharaff]]
* [[奥斯卡最佳原创音乐奖|最佳原创音乐奖]] – [[Alfred_Newman_(composer)|Alfred Newman]] and [[Ken_Darby|Ken Darby]]
* [[奧斯卡最佳混音獎|最佳混音獎]] – [[Carlton_W._Faulkner|Carlton W. Faulkner]]; 20th Century Fox Sound Department

